## Requirements

- Node.js 20+
- pnpm 9+

## Installation

```bash
pnpm install
node node_modules/.pnpm/electron@*/node_modules/electron/install.js
pnpm run build
```

## Running

```bash
pnpm dev
```

Discovery Telescope web interface (non-browser):

```bash
pnpm kesif:web
```

API: `http://127.0.0.1:3921`

