## Project structure

- `packages/teleskop-core` — shared models
- `packages/kesif-durbunu` — crawler, index, search API
- `packages/teleskop-assistant` — local assistant (rule-based)
- `apps/desktop` — Electron browser
- `apps/kesif-web` — external search site
- `apps/mobile` — Flutter (Phase 2)

